high_descs: Go to the counter on your left.
Pick up the knife next to the green scrub.
Turn around and walk to the brown table on your right.
Cut the bread loaf on the table into slices.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door and put the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and go to the table.
Pick up one slice of bread.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Open the fridge door, put the bread in the fridge and refrigerate for 5 minutes. Open the fridge door and take out the bread slice. Close the fridge door.
Turn around and go to the brown table.
Put the bread slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Refrigerate a bread slice and put it on a table.

high_descs: Turn left and step forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn around and walk forward and right to face the table.
Cut the bread on the table into slices.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and walk forward to face the table.
Pick up a slice of bread on the table.
Turn around and cross the room to face the fridge.
Cool the bread slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn around and walk forward to face the table.
Place the slice of bread on the table.
anns.task_desc: To cool a slice of bread and place it on the table.
